              "link": "",
              "size": 0
            }
          },
          "title2": "<br><br>CAD/CAM/CAE Drafting and Modelling",
          "caption2": "<b>Take a look at our extensive<br> list of products.</b>\n<br>Good graphics design solutions to communication problem can improve the flow of information in society and therefore ,substantially and positively affect the education ,social ell being and the daily enjoyment of life.in addition,good graphic design solution can also have a positive economic impact.we make sure that you get well-versed in learning graphics to design your solution",
          "button2": "<a data-app-btn=\"true\" href=\"https://mobirise.com\" class=\"mbr-buttons__btn btn btn-wrap btn-xs-lg btn-default\">LEARN MORE</a>",
          "media3": {
            "image": {
              "active": true,
              "src": "@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/eb34b50f2ef4053ed1584d05fb1d449ee576e1d01fac104496f9c87ca1edb0be-640.jpg-1-600x262.jpg",
